 were necessary, most would abandon the endeavor.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 22, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBlxPIm5", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 112, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8714125, "raw_content": "They do not respect our flag, our history, our people and our country! President Trump has to kick all these fucking assholes out of America. \n\nEvery GOP congress member who cried about SCOTUS ruling on birthright citizenship better vote to change the definition of the \"subject\" to the jurisdiction to mean only US citizens and LPR. The test for subject to the jurisdiction must be the mother's allegiance to which country, and only US citizens and LPR swore allegiance to the Flag of the United States of America, and to the Republic for which it stands, one Nation under God, indivisible, with liberty and justice for all.", "author": "Tomis_4", "created": 1783226023397, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Secession2030", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "America became the most powerful country in the world because we took care of our own. We are proud to be Americans and respect our heritage. Immigrants used to desperately want to be Americans and sacrificed everything to be here. Now, we have too many fucking losers in the country.", "last_comment_created": 17832